        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>Pick the timeWindow value based on the user&apos;s phrasing:

   - &quot;recent&quot;, &quot;recently&quot;, &quot;lately&quot;, &quot;this month&quot;
        -&gt; LAST_30_DAYS

   - &quot;this week&quot;, &quot;this past week&quot;, &quot;yesterday&quot;, &quot;today&quot;
        -&gt; LAST_7_DAYS

   - &quot;summary&quot;, &quot;recap&quot;, &quot;overview&quot;, &quot;tell me about&quot;
     (default when no time qualifier)
        -&gt; THIS_YEAR

   - &quot;this quarter&quot;, &quot;Q1&quot;, &quot;Q2&quot;, &quot;Q3&quot;, &quot;Q4&quot;
        -&gt; THIS_QUARTER

   - &quot;last month&quot;, &quot;previous month&quot;
        -&gt; LAST_MONTH

   - &quot;this year&quot;, &quot;year to date&quot;, &quot;YTD&quot;
        -&gt; THIS_YEAR

   - &quot;all&quot;, &quot;everything&quot;, &quot;every&quot;, &quot;full&quot;, &quot;total&quot;, &quot;ever&quot;,
     &quot;all time&quot;, &quot;from the start&quot;
        -&gt; ALL_TIME

   - &quot;last X days/weeks/months&quot; (specific number)
        -&gt; CUSTOM_DAYS with customDays = X (convert weeks*7,
           months*30 if user uses them)

If user gives no time qualifier at all, default to THIS_YEAR.</description>
            <developerName>instruction_1_1777795500125</developerName>
            <language xsi:nil="true"/>
