       Service Agent:  MUST pass verifiedUserId (from STEP 0).
                       Required — do NOT omit on Service Agent.

   timeWindow     = the token chosen in Instruction 3
   customDays     = positive integer (only when timeWindow
                    = CUSTOM_DAYS)</description>
