        <genAiPluginInstructions>
            <description>After delivering the summary, END the conversation. Do NOT
ask &quot;anything else?&quot;. Do NOT propose creating new records. Do
NOT ask if the user wants more detail. The user can ask a
follow-up themselves if they want.

If the user DOES send a follow-up like &quot;tell me about a
different doctor&quot;, treat it as a fresh trigger of this topic
and start again from Instruction 2 (skip Instruction 1 — the
user is still authorized).</description>
